# ===================================
# Supabase Setup Instructions:
# ===================================
# 1. Go to Supabase Dashboard > Settings > Database
# 2. Reset your database password if needed
# 3. Copy the password and replace [YOUR-PASSWORD] in both DATABASE_URL and DIRECT_DATABASE_URL above
# 4. Copy this file to app/.env: cp env.sample app/.env
# 5. Run: cd app && pnpm prisma migrate dev
# 6. Run: cd app && pnpm prisma generate

# ===================================
# Database Connection Explained:
# ===================================
# DATABASE_URL: Uses Transaction Pooler (port 6543) - for app connections
# DIRECT_DATABASE_URL: Uses Direct Connection (port 5432) - for migrations
# This setup is required for Prisma to work properly with Supabase

# ===================================
# Vercel Setup Instructions:
# ===================================
# 1. Install Vercel CLI: npm i -g vercel
# 2. Run: vercel login
# 3. In the app directory, run: vercel
# 4. Set environment variables in Vercel dashboard or use: vercel env add
# 5. For production, set NEXTAUTH_URL to https://invoice.94forward.ca

